<topic id = "AENAP70A1406028006">
<title>
Venturi plug inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
Check that venturi plug passage is not clogged.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If venturi plug passage is clogged, clean or replace venturi plug.
</ptxt>
