<topic id = "AENAP70A1406028007">
<title>
Valve head radial runout
</title>
<ptxt>
Check each valve for radial runout with a dial gauge and “V” block. To check runout, rotate valve slowly. If runout exceeds its limit, replace valve.
</ptxt>
